  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_65",
    "english": "Demon. She works as an informant in Amahara. She has been living for a long time, so she is very knowledgeable. She sells her information not just to Taimanins, but also to politicians, demons, etc. Her activities from being an informant have earned her the Nomads' quiet enmity, putting her life at risk.\n\nAlthough no one has seen it, there are rumors that her skills rival those of Nomad's Hell Knight, Ingrid. She can control Demonic Insects by blowing a bit of demonic power into insects.",
    "japanese": "Demon. She works as an informant in Amahara. She has been living for a long time, so she is very knowledgeable. She sells her information not just to Taimanins, but also to politicians, demons, etc. Her activities from being an informant have earned her the Nomads' quiet enmity, putting her life at risk.\n\nAlthough no one has seen it, there are rumors that her skills rival those of Nomad's Hell Knight, Ingrid. She can control Demonic Insects by blowing a bit of demonic power into insects.",
    "korean": "Demon. She works as an informant in Amahara. She has been living for a long time, so she is very knowledgeable. She sells her information not just to Taimanins, but also to politicians, demons, etc. Her activities from being an informant have earned her the Nomads' quiet enmity, putting her life at risk.\n\nAlthough no one has seen it, there are rumors that her skills rival those of Nomad's Hell Knight, Ingrid. She can control Demonic Insects by blowing a bit of demonic power into insects.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Demon. She works as an informant in Amahara. She has been living for a long time, so she is very knowledgeable. She sells her information not just to Taimanins, but also to politicians, demons, etc. Her activities from being an informant have earned her the Nomads' quiet enmity, putting her life at risk.\n\nAlthough no one has seen it, there are rumors that her skills rival those of Nomad's Hell Knight, Ingrid. She can control Demonic Insects by blowing a bit of demonic power into insects.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Demon. She works as an informant in Amahara. She has been living for a long time, so she is very knowledgeable. She sells her information not just to Taimanins, but also to politicians, demons, etc. Her activities from being an informant have earned her the Nomads' quiet enmity, putting her life at risk.\n\nAlthough no one has seen it, there are rumors that her skills rival those of Nomad's Hell Knight, Ingrid. She can control Demonic Insects by blowing a bit of demonic power into insects.",
    "spanish": "Demon. She works as an informant in Amahara. She has been living for a long time, so she is very knowledgeable. She sells her information not just to Taimanins, but also to politicians, demons, etc. Her activities from being an informant have earned her the Nomads' quiet enmity, putting her life at risk.\n\nAlthough no one has seen it, there are rumors that her skills rival those of Nomad's Hell Knight, Ingrid. She can control Demonic Insects by blowing a bit of demonic power into insects."
